FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Got questions about our blockchain info finder? We've got answers.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What is this blockchain information finder app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app is a cutting-edge tool designed to help you discover and stay updated on the latest blockchain information, including new projects, technologies, and market trends.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How does the app find new blockchain information?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We use advanced algorithms and AI to scan multiple sources, including news outlets, social media, and blockchain networks, to aggregate and analyze the most recent and relevant blockchain data.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Is this app suitable for both beginners and experienced blockchain enthusiasts?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Absolutely! Our app caters to users of all levels. Beginners can learn about blockchain basics, while experienced users can dive deep into complex technical information and market analysis.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: How often is the information updated?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Our app updates in real-time, ensuring you always have access to the most current blockchain information as soon as it becomes available.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Can I customize the type of blockchain information I receive?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Yes, you can personalize your feed by selecting specific blockchain networks, projects, or topics you're interested in. This way, you'll only see the information most relevant to you.

ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Our app uses advanced algorithms and AI to scan multiple blockchain networks, news sources, social media platforms, and research publications. It then filters and categorizes the information to present you with relevant and up-to-date blockchain data tailored to your interests.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Absolutely! BlockchainInfoFinder is designed for users of all levels. Whether you're a blockchain novice or an experienced professional, our app provides easy-to-understand information and allows you to customize your experience based on your knowledge and preferences.

ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, you can! BlockchainInfoFinder allows you to create personalized watchlists for specific blockchain projects, cryptocurrencies, or topics of interest. You'll receive real-time updates and notifications about your chosen items, ensuring you never miss important information.
